<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Erro interno - VendMaster</title>

    <style>
        :root {
            --vm-blue: #0757c8;
            --vm-blue-dark: #063b91;
            --vm-blue-deep: #042f7c;
            --vm-blue-soft: #eaf3ff;
            --vm-green: #35b24a;
            --vm-green-dark: #188331;
            --vm-text: #102033;
            --vm-muted: #64748b;
            --vm-card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
            --vm-shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html,
        body {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 88% 8%, rgba(7, 87, 200, 0.15), transparent 24%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 2% 96%, rgba(53, 178, 74, 0.15), transparent 24%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 85% 18%, rgba(53, 178, 74, 0.12), transparent 28%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 18% 88%, rgba(7, 87, 200, 0.12), transparent 30%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #f7fbff 0%, #eaf5ff 46%, #f5fff7 100%);
            color: var(--vm-text);
        }

        svg {
            display: block;
            width: 1em;
            height: 1em;
            fill: currentColor;
        }

        .error-page {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 34px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-page::before,
        .error-page::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 999px;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .error-page::before {
            width: 420px;
            height: 420px;
            top: -155px;
            right: -110px;
            background: rgba(7, 87, 200, 0.12);
        }

        .error-page::after {
            width: 320px;
            height: 320px;
            left: -120px;
            bottom: -120px;
            background: rgba(53, 178, 74, 0.14);
        }

        .error-card {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            width: min(100%, 760px);
            padding: 56px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
            border-radius: 36px;
            background: var(--vm-card);
            box-shadow: var(--vm-shadow);
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
        }

        .error-brand-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .error-logo-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-radius: 22px;
            background: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .error-logo {
            display: block;
            width: auto;
            max-width: 240px;
            height: 50px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .error-icon {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 78px;
            height: 78px;
            border-radius: 26px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--vm-blue), var(--vm-green));
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(7, 87, 200, 0.26);
        }

        .error-icon svg {
            width: 38px;
            height: 38px;
        }

        .error-code {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 9px 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(7, 87, 200, 0.1), rgba(53, 178, 74, 0.12));
            color: var(--vm-blue);
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .error-card h1 {
            max-width: 620px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: var(--vm-text);
            font-size: clamp(2.45rem, 5.4vw, 4.7rem);
            line-height: 0.98;
            letter-spacing: -0.07em;
            font-weight: 950;
        }

        .error-card p {
            max-width: 560px;
            margin: 24px auto 0;
            color: var(--vm-muted);
            font-size: 1.12rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .error-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 34px;
        }

        .error-button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            min-height: 56px;
            padding: 0 24px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--vm-blue), var(--vm-green));
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 0.98rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(7, 87, 200, 0.28);
            transition:
                transform 0.2s ease,
                box-shadow 0.2s ease,
                filter 0.2s ease;
        }

        .error-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            filter: brightness(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 24px 46px rgba(7, 87, 200, 0.34);
        }

        .error-button svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
        }

        .error-button-secondary {
            background: #ffffff;
            color: var(--vm-blue);
            border: 1px solid rgba(7, 87, 200, 0.16);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.07);
        }

        .error-button-secondary:hover {
            color: var(--vm-green-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
        }

        .error-hint {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 14px;
            margin-top: 38px;
        }

        .error-hint-item {
            padding: 18px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
            text-align: left;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
        }

        .error-hint-item strong {
            display: block;
            color: var(--vm-text);
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .error-hint-item span {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 5px;
            color: var(--vm-muted);
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            line-height: 1.42;
        }

        @media (min-width: 721px) {
            .error-brand-row {
                flex-direction: row;
                gap: 12px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 720px) {
            .error-page {
                align-items: flex-start;
                padding: 22px;
            }

            .error-card {
                padding: 34px 22px;
                border-radius: 28px;
            }

            .error-logo {
                max-width: 190px;
                height: 44px;
            }

            .error-icon {
                width: 68px;
                height: 68px;
                border-radius: 22px;
            }

            .error-icon svg {
                width: 32px;
                height: 32px;
            }

            .error-card h1 {
                font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 12vw, 3.35rem);
            }

            .error-card p {
                margin-top: 18px;
                font-size: 1rem;
                line-height: 1.65;
            }

            .error-actions {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                margin-top: 26px;
            }

            .error-button {
                width: 100%;
                min-height: 54px;
            }

            .error-hint {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                margin-top: 28px;
            }

            .error-hint-item {
                text-align: center;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 420px) {
            .error-page {
                padding: 16px;
            }

            .error-card {
                padding: 28px 18px;
                border-radius: 24px;
            }

            .error-logo {
                height: 40px;
            }

            .error-code {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main class="error-page">
        <section class="error-card" aria-labelledby="error-title">
            <div class="error-brand-row">
                <a href="/" class="error-logo-link" aria-label="Voltar para a página inicial do VendMaster">
                    <img src="/images/brand/logo.webp" alt="VendMaster" class="error-logo">
                </a>

                <div class="error-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" aria-label="">
                        <path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10A10.011 10.011 0 0 0 12 2Zm1 15h-2v-2h2Zm0-4h-2V7h2Z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>

                <div class="error-code">Erro 500</div>
            </div>

            <h1 id="error-title">Algo não saiu como esperado.</h1>

            <p>
                Encontramos uma instabilidade interna ao carregar esta página.
                Tente novamente em alguns instantes ou volte para a página inicial do VendMaster.
            </p>

            <div class="error-actions" aria-label="Ações para continuar navegando">
                <a href="/" class="error-button">
                    Voltar para a página inicial
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                        <path d="M12.293 5.293 13.707 3.88 21.828 12l-8.121 8.121-1.414-1.414L18 13H2v-2h16z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </a>

                <a href="/login" class="error-button error-button-secondary">
                    Ir para o login
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="error-hint" aria-label="Sugestões">
                <div class="error-hint-item">
                    <strong>Tente novamente</strong>
                    <span>Atualize a página em alguns instantes.</span>
                </div>

                <div class="error-hint-item">
                    <strong>Volte ao início</strong>
                    <span>Acesse a página inicial e continue navegando.</span>
                </div>

                <div class="error-hint-item">
                    <strong>Precisa de ajuda?</strong>
                    <span>Entre em contato com o suporte se o erro continuar.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>

</html>